<i>adverb</i>: 한사코 [한ː사코], 추근추근 [추근추근], 악착같이 [악착까치], 뭉글뭉글 [뭉글뭉글], 뭉게뭉게 [뭉게뭉게], 무럭무럭 [무렁무럭], 꾸준히 [꾸준히], 굳이 [구지] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>adverb</i><br>
<dt>한사코 [한ː사코]</dt><br>
<dd>persistently; desperately</dd><br>
<dd>계속해서 있는 힘을 다하여.</dd><br>
<dd>Continuously with all one's might.</dd><br>
<dt>추근추근 [추근추근]</dt><br>
<dd>tenaciously; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>성질이나 태도가 끈질긴 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>With a tenacious nature or attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>악착같이 [악착까치]</dt><br>
<dd>perseveringly; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>매우 억세고 끈질기게.</dd><br>
<dd>With a very rough and tenacious attitude.</dd><br>
<dt>뭉글뭉글 [뭉글뭉글]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in a lumpy and slithery state</dd><br>
<dd>덩이진 물건이 물렁물렁하고 매우 미끄러운 느낌.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which something clotted feels soft and very slippery.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in clouds; densely</dd><br>
<dd>구름이나 연기가 뭉쳐서 잇따라 나오는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of clouds or smoke appearing one after another and forming masses.</dd><br>
<dd>3. one after another; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 감정이 잇따라 자꾸 떠오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which ideas or feelings occur in succession.</dd><br>
<dt>뭉게뭉게 [뭉게뭉게]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in clouds; densely</dd><br>
<dd>구름이나 연기가 잇달아 나오며 덩어리를 이루는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>A word describing the movement of clouds or smoke appearing one after another and forming masses.</dd><br>
<dd>2. persistently</dd><br>
<dd>생각이나 느낌이 자꾸 일어나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which ideas, feelings, etc., occur continuously.</dd><br>
<dt>무럭무럭 [무렁무럭]</dt><br>
<dd>1. rapidly</dd><br>
<dd>순조롭고 힘차게 잘 자라는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the state of growing up well and healthily.</dd><br>
<dd>2. in the manner of rising into the air</dd><br>
<dd>김, 연기, 냄새 등이 자꾸 많이 피어오르는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner that steam, smoke, smell, etc., rises in large amounts and continuously.</dd><br>
<dd>3. persistently</dd><br>
<dd>느낌, 생각 등이 마음속에서 자꾸 일어나는 모양.</dd><br>
<dd>In a state in which ideas, feelings, etc., occur in one's mind continuously.</dd><br>
<dt>꾸준히 [꾸준히]</dt><br>
<dd>steadily; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>거의 변함이 없이 한결같이.</dd><br>
<dd>Consistently.</dd><br>
<dt>굳이 [구지]</dt><br>
<dd>1. in the manner of taking trouble</dd><br>
<dd>마음을 써서 일부러.</dd><br>
<dd>In the manner of caring about something specially.</dd><br>
<dd>2. obstinately; persistently</dd><br>
<dd>고집을 부려서.</dd><br>
<dd>Insistently.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>